# Signature Equipment

Heroes carry many weapons and wear various armors across their careers. But every legendary figure has *the* weapon—the named blade, the ancestral shield, the staff that never leaves their side. Signature equipment isn't just mechanically superior gear. It's the equipment that defines your character visually and narratively, that grows alongside you, that cannot be truly lost.

